"ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1002156, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Glory be to Him who is aware of what the hearts and minds strive to obtain! Glory be to Him who knows the exact count of the sins! Glory be to Him from whose view nothing in the heavens and the earths is concealed! Glory be to the Loving Lord! Glory be to the Unique Single! Glory be to the Greatest Great! Glory be to Him Who does not, without reason or occasion, bear hard upon the ’men of means’!", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Paak-tar hai Woh jo dilo’n ke bhed (raaz) jaanta hai. Paak-tar hai woh jo gunaho’n ko shumaar karta hai. Paak-tar hai woh jo jis par aasmaano aur zameeno ki panahiya makhfi aur ojal nahin. Paak-tar hai mohabbat karne waala Parwardigaar. Paak-tar hai woh jo tanha o yakta hai. Paak-tar hai woh jo bada hai sab se bada hai. Paak-tar hai woh jo apni hukumat mein rehne waalo’n par ziyaadati nahin karta.", "Urdu": "پاک تر ہے وہ جو دلوں کے بھید جانتا ہے پاک تر ہے وہ جو گناہوں کو شمار کرتا ہے پاک تر ہے وہ جس پر آسمانوں اور زمینوں کی پہنائیاں اور وسعتیں اوجھل نہیں پاک تر ہے محبت کرنے والا پروردگار پاک تر ہے وہ جو تنہا و یکتا ہے پاک تر ہے وہ جو بڑا ہے سب سے بڑا ہے پاک تر ہے وہ جو اپنی حکومت میں رہنے والوں پر زیادتی نہیں کرتا۔", "RArabic": "SUB-HAANA MAIY YA’LAMO JAWAARE-HAL QOLOOBE. SUB-HAANA MAIY YOHSEE A’DA-DAZ ZONOO-BE. SUB-HAANA MAL LAA YAKH-FAA A’LAIY-HE KHAAFE-YATUN FIS SAMAA-WAATE WAL ARA-ZEENA. SUB-HAA-NAR RABBIL WA-DOODE. SUB-HAA-NAL A’ZEEM-IL AA’ZAME. SUB-HAANA MAL LAA YA’TADEE A’LAA AHLE MAMLA-KATE-HI.", "ArabicText1": "سُبْحَانَ مَنْ يَّعْلَمُ جَوَارِحَ الْقُلُوْبِ۔ سُبْحَانَ مَنْ يُّحْصِيْ عَدَدَ الذُّنُوْبِ۔ سُبْحَانَ مَنْ لَّا يَخْفٰى عَلَيْهِ خَافِيَةٌ فِي السَّمَاوَاتِ وَالْاَرَضِيْنَ۔ سُبْحَانَ الرَّبِّ الْوَدُوْدِ۔ سُبْحَانَ الْفَرْدِ الْوِتْرِ۔ سُبْحَانَ الْعَظِيْمِ الْاَعْظَمِ۔ سُبْحَانَ مَنْ لَّا يَعْتَدِيْ عَلٰى اَهْلِ مَمْلَكَتِهٖ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1002503, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Glory be to Him who does not bring down any kind of punishment upon the people needlessly! Glory be to the kind Compassionate! Glory be to the Oft-Forgiving Merciful! Glory be to the Omnipotent Generous! Glory be to the indulgent Liberal! Glory be to the Discerning Wise! Glory be to the Comprehending All-Wise!", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Paak-tar hai woh jo zameen par rehne waalo’n ko tarah tarah ka azaab nahi deta. Paak-tar hai woh jo mohabbat o ehsaan waala hai. Paak-tar hai woh jo maher-baan o rahem waala hai. Paak-tar hai woh jo ghaalib-tar hai bohot dene waala. Paak-tar hai woh jo buzurgi waala burdbaar hai. Paak-tar hai woh jo dekhne aur jaanne waala hai. Paak-tar hai woh jo baseerat o wus’at waala hai.", "Urdu": " پاک تر ہے وہ جو زمین پر رہنے والوں کو طرح طرح کا عذاب نہیں دیتا پاک تر ہے وہ جو محبت والا احسان والا ہے پاک تر ہے وہ جو مہربان رحم والا ہے پاک تر ہے وہ جو غالب تر ہے بہت دینے والا پاک تر ہے وہ جو بزرگی والا بردبار ہے پاک تر ہے وہ جو دیکھنے والا جاننے والا ہے پاک تر ہے وہ جو بصیرت و وسعت والا ہے پاک تر ہے اللہ دن کے نکل آنے پر۔", "RArabic": "SUB-HAANA MAL LAA YO-AAKHE-ZO AH-LAL ARZE BE-ALWAA-NIL A’ZAABE. SUB-HAA-NAL HANNAA-NIL MANNAA-NE. SUB-HAA-NAR RAOO-FIR RAHEE-ME. SUB-HAA-NAL JABBAA-RIL JAWAA-DE. SUB-HAA-NAL KAREE-MIL HALEE-ME. SUB-HAA-NAL BASEE-RIL A’LEE-ME.", "ArabicText1": "سُبْحَانَ مَنْ لَّا يُؤَاخِذُ اَهْلَ الْاَرْضِ بِاَلْوَانِ الْعَذَابِ۔ سُبْحَانَ الْحَنَّانِ الْمَنَّانِ۔ سُبْحَانَ الرَّءُوْفِ الرَّحِيْمِ۔ سُبْحَانَ الْجَبَّارِ الْجَوَادِ۔ سُبْحَانَ الْكَرِيْمِ الْحَلِيْمِ۔ سُبْحَانَ الْبَصِيْرِ الْعَلِيْمِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1002504, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Glory be to Allah at the time of Daybreak! Glory be to Allah at the time of sunset! Glory be to Allah in the zero hours of the departing night and in the twilight of the dawning day! For Him alone is the praise, might, greatness and omnipotence. He is there with every breath and every twinkle of an eye, and every moment is already registered in His all-embracing awareness. Glory be to Thee for the infinite range that covers Thy Books! Glory be to Thee, Glory that is equal to Thy Arsh in weight, measure and value! Glory be to Thee! Glory be to Thee! Glory be to Thee!", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Paak-tar hai Allah din ke nikal aane par. Paak-tar hai Allah raat ke chale jaane aur din ke aa jaane par, Uske liye hamd o buzurgi o badaayi aur bulandi hai har saans ke saath, aankh jabak-ne ke saath aur har ghadi mein jo Uske ilm mein guzar chuki hai. Teri zaat paak hai us par jo Teri kitaab mein shumaar kiya gaya hai. Teri zaat paak hai Tere arsh ke wazn ke saath. Tu paak-tar hai, Tu paak-tar hai, Tu paak-tar hai.", "Urdu": "پاک تر ہے اللہ دن کے چھپ جانے پر پاک تر ہے اللہ رات کے چلے جانے اور دن کے آجانے پر اسی کے لئے حمد بزرگی بڑائی اور بلندی ہے ہر سانس کے ساتھ آنکھ جھپکنے کے ساتھ اور ہر گھڑی میں جو اس کے علم میں گزرچکی ہے تیری ذات پاک ہے اس پر جو کچھ تیری کتاب میں شمار کیا گیا ہے تیری ذات پاک ہے تیرے عرش کے وزن کے ساتھ تو پاک تر ہے تو پاک تر ہے تو پاک تر ہے۔", "RArabic": "SUB-HAA-NAL BASEE-RIL WAASE-E’. SUB-HAA-NAL-LAAHE A’LAA IQBAA-LIN NAHAA-RE. SUB-HAA-NAL-LAAHE A’LAA IDBAA-RIN NAHAA-RE. SUB-HAA-NAL-LAAHE A’LAA IDBAA-RIL LAIY-LE WA IQBAA-LIN NAHAA-RE WA LAHUL HAMDO WAL MAJDO WAL A’ZA-MATO WAL KIBRE-YAA-O MA-A’ KULLE NAFSEEN WA KULLO TAR-FA-TE A’IY-NIN WA KULLO LAM-HATIN SABAQA FEE I’LME-HI. SUB-HAA-NAKA MIL-AMAA AHSAA KETAA-BOKA. SUB-HAA-NAKA ZE-NATA A’R-SHEKA SUB-HAA-NAKA, SUB-HAA-NAKA, SUB-HAA-NAKA.", "ArabicText1": "سُبْحَانَ الْبَصِيْرِ الْوَاسِعِ۔ سُبْحَانَ اللهِ عَلٰى اِقْبَالِ النَّهَارِ۔ سُبْحَانَ اللهِ عَلٰى اِدْبَارِ النَّهَارِ۔ سُبْحَانَ اللهِ عَلٰى اِدْبَارِ اللَّيْلِ وَاِقْبَالِ النَّهَارِ وَلَهُ الْحَمْدُ وَالْمَجْدُ وَالْعَظَمَةُ وَالْكِبْرِيَاءُ مَعَ كُلِّ نَفْسٍ وَكُلُّ طَرْفَةِ عَيْنٍ وَكُلُّ لَمْحَةٍ سَبَقَ فِيْ عِلْمِهٖ۔ سُبْحَانَكَ مِلْاَمَا اَحْصٰى كِتَابُكَ۔ سُبْحَانَكَ زِنَةَ عَرْشِكَ سُبْحَانَكَ سُبْحَانَكَ سُبْحَانَكَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedS